{"type": "article", "id": 26533, "title": "那些被负能量小事毁掉的一天，一次让你看够", "description": "结尾不错，记得看完。", "date": "2016-05-08T10:14:36Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 11405, "name": "好奇心研究所"}], "category": 3, "author": 130547, "comment_count": 36, "praise_count": 492, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021528310NzbIq4ySRVHTLao.gif", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">好奇心研究所的微博（@好奇心研究所）和微信公众号（ID：QLab42）全面上线啦，关注就可以与所长亲密接触。  <b><br></b></p>\n<p class=\"\"><b>1. 没睡好。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152810eyBFGgUM6xfDaLWn.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>2. 被邻居装修的电钻声，或者蚊子嗡嗡嗡嗡嗡嗡嗡吵醒。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152811h9E68SbRDmk5eCi7.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>3. 而闹钟没有响。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152812S8kgDAwMf1HK3si7.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>4. 工作群有鲜红的 @。和床单染上的姨妈很配。<br></b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152813oyRaY7XZ4dSg6hBl.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><b>5. 按照惯例，差不多是“甲方凌晨 3 点发了封邮件：第 11 遍方案仍旧未能抓住我司气质精髓。你到底行不行？”<br></b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152814ARDcXGI6fMBzgHKw.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>6. 而，昨晚发给 TA 的信息，依然没有回。<br></b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152815kymIR83VsXCtcr16.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>7. 吐司和牛奶都吃光了。楼下鸡蛋灌饼大叔没出现。<br></b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152815FJPrpEwvutYjkHW1.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>8. 凑合泡一杯咖啡，溅到白衬衫上。  <br></b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152816oQ1P0Kzvy8AgFJen.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>9. 胖了一斤。\r\n\r\n头好油。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152817T7sb1HflmtpCaFvq.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>10. Uber 司机不认路，绕一个大圈，骂导航。<br></b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021528188TEFuwKdQxAvas0f.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>11. 早知道反正会迟到，还不如洗个头。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152819KjbSHGtMnsU2iY5L.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>12. 电梯里遇到碧池，说，第 12 版方案你准备怎么改？</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152819NY3QxogKHV2f6yW4.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>13. 默默照镜子，忽然意识到：……我今天穿这么丑？！</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152820Ev6TuqcUdaWlFPQf.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>14. 说好的快递，没，有，来。  <br></b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152823yhGzYJtD1Ljvp3Co.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>15. 完全忘记今天是报销截止日。发票没有带。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152824mBlu5qXEoZxVQDRc.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>16. 好了，Wifi 连不上。<br></b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152825uCht5xZ9EDjqQPSJ.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>17. 我不干了。玩手机。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152826cbpWxzwjr9lYSedG.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>18. 手机掉地，屏碎了。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152827SiBGkHr8jbaqYvRt.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>19. 其实还有可能更糟。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152827qIa1QOGZN8H2JFT9.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>20. 比如今天是法定节假日。只是我加班。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152828SNjWQFgYiAt2cBfG.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>21. 人生总想说呵呵。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152829iuZKDkPMURoO6dT2.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>22. 世界充满负能量。<br></b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152829Ov16DItxgkeG83Bn.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>23. 不过，话说回来，如果你有功夫被小事烦成这样。还是有一件好事——说明一件大事都没发生。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152830DiXtYGUQB7Fjzd8p.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>动图来自：<a href=\"http://giphy.com/\">giphy</a></p>\n<p><i><a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/labs.html\">好奇心研究所</a></i><em>是好奇心日报的一个调查栏目，这是一个探讨各种生活方式问题的互动平台，它针对的可能是生活方式的变化和潮流，也可能是某个品牌的服务。你可以在这里投票、吐槽、表明态度。</em></p>\n\n\n"}